&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Alt+Tab &lt;/strong&gt;

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The keyboard shortcut is most often used to switch between open programs in Microsoft Windows 10.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Alt + S&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;​Alt+S is a keyboard&lt;strong&gt; shortcut most often used to open the slide show settings in PowerPoint.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Ctrl + S&lt;/span&gt;​&lt;/strong&gt;
